</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">A REBB drops.  Who needs it more?  A monk with Fangs and a GMU, or a beastie with a slp and wlk?</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
