<br />
Both need it, so both can roll on it.
<br />

<br />
NBG doesn't mean "He can get more benefit out of it than you, so he gets it." It means "Casters and priests don't get to roll on the REBB. The melees do." It's the same method everyone uses in pickup groups, at least on my server.
